# ResourceManagerSystem

## Purpose
One-shot initialization system. On the first frame, loads all textures, fonts, shaders, UI
layouts, sound clips, JSON assets, 3D models, and render targets from `Assets/Engine/ResourcesManifest.json`
and `Assets/App/ResourcesManifest.json`, then creates ResourceMapSingletonComponent containing the fully
populated asset maps. No-op on all subsequent frames (presence check guards early exit).

Render targets are pathless manifest entries (`{id, width, height}`): the created offscreen target is
stored in the render-target map and its colour buffer is registered in the texture map under the same
UUID, so 2D draws can sample the 3D pass's output as an ordinary texture (ADR 0007).

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| ResourceMapSingletonComponent | read | Presence-check only; if present, system exits immediately |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| ResourceMapSingletonComponent | add (deferred) | Created once; holds texture, shader, font, UI layout, sound clip, parsed JSON asset, 3D model, and render-target maps keyed by UUID |
